###############################################################################
# OBJECTIVE
###############################################################################
Conduct comprehensive visual QA across all screens and devices; verify design consistency, animation quality, and overall user experience; prepare for client approval.

###############################################################################
# SCOPE
###############################################################################
Visual and functional QA:
  1. Cross-screen consistency verification
  2. Animation quality check
  3. Cross-browser testing
  4. Cross-device testing (mobile, tablet, desktop)
  5. Theme testing (light/dark mode)
  6. Edge case testing
  7. Final build verification

###############################################################################
# DELIVERABLES
###############################################################################
output:
  - QA report: totem/instances/navitrack/sprints/44/S44-QA-REPORT.md
  - Screenshots of all screens (light/dark themes)
  - Bug list (if any issues found)

###############################################################################
# QA TESTING MATRIX
###############################################################################

1. Screen-by-Screen Visual QA:

For each of 8 screens:
  - [ ] Glass effects render correctly
  - [ ] Glow effects visible and smooth
  - [ ] Animations play correctly
  - [ ] Spacing and layout correct
  - [ ] Typography correct (sizes, weights)
  - [ ] Icons positioned correctly
  - [ ] Color usage consistent with design system
  - [ ] Hover states work
  - [ ] Focus states visible
  - [ ] Disabled states styled correctly
  - [ ] Loading states work (if applicable)
  - [ ] Error states work (if applicable)

Screens to test:
  1. login-screen.tsx
  2. objects-screen.tsx
  3. settings-screen.tsx
  4. tracking-screen.tsx
  5. reports-screen.tsx
  6. map-screen.tsx
  7. object-details-screen.tsx
  8. select-objects-screen.tsx
  9. account-security-screen.tsx

2. Animation Quality Check:

For all animated elements:
  - [ ] glass-input-pulse: Smooth, subtle pulsing
  - [ ] rainbow-glow-pulse: Smooth rainbow effect, not jarring
  - [ ] app-bg-pulse: Smooth background breathing effect
  - [ ] Hover transitions: 280ms smooth
  - [ ] Focus transitions: Instant or very fast
  - [ ] All animations 60fps (no jank)
  - [ ] Reduced motion: All animations disabled when enabled

3. Cross-Browser Testing:

Test in:
  - [ ] Chrome (latest)
  - [ ] Safari (latest)
  - [ ] Firefox (latest)
  - [ ] Edge (latest)

Verify:
  - Glass effects render correctly (backdrop-filter support)
  - Animations play smoothly
  - Colors correct in all browsers
  - Layout consistent

4. Cross-Device Testing:

Desktop:
  - [ ] 1920x1080 (Full HD)
  - [ ] 1366x768 (Common laptop)
  - [ ] 2560x1440 (QHD)

Tablet:
  - [ ] iPad (1024x768)
  - [ ] iPad Pro (1366x1024)

Mobile:
  - [ ] iPhone 12/13 (390x844)
  - [ ] iPhone SE (375x667)
  - [ ] Android (various sizes)

Verify all:
  - Responsive design works
  - Glass effects scaled appropriately
  - Touch targets min 44x44px
  - No horizontal scroll
  - Safe areas respected (notches)

5. Theme Testing:

Light Theme:
  - [ ] All screens render correctly
  - [ ] Glass effects visible
  - [ ] Glow effects visible
  - [ ] Text contrast sufficient
  - [ ] Background animation inverted correctly

Dark Theme:
  - [ ] All screens render correctly
  - [ ] Glass effects visible (darker opacity)
  - [ ] Glow effects more pronounced
  - [ ] Text contrast sufficient
  - [ ] Background animation dark overlay

6. Edge Cases:

Test:
  - [ ] Empty states (no data)
  - [ ] Loading states
  - [ ] Error states (network, validation)
  - [ ] Very long text (truncation)
  - [ ] Special characters in text
  - [ ] Rapid interactions (spam clicking)
  - [ ] Screen rotation (mobile)
  - [ ] Landscape mode (mobile)

7. Build Verification:

Final checks:
  - [ ] pnpm run build: Zero errors
  - [ ] pnpm run lint: Zero warnings
  - [ ] TypeScript: Zero errors
  - [ ] dist/ bundle size reasonable (< 500KB gzip for JS)
  - [ ] No console errors in production build
  - [ ] Source maps generated
  - [ ] Service worker (PWA) works

8. PWA & Lighthouse Testing:

PWA checks:
  - [ ] manifest.json correct (NaviTrack icons 192/512)
  - [ ] apple-touch-icon present
  - [ ] theme-color correct (#2d8a3e)
  - [ ] Service worker caching works (navitrack-app-v3)
  - [ ] Offline fallback page works
  - [ ] Install prompt works on mobile

Lighthouse audit:
  - [ ] Performance: ≥ 90
  - [ ] Accessibility: ≥ 95
  - [ ] Best Practices: ≥ 90
  - [ ] SEO: ≥ 90
  - [ ] PWA: ✓ Installable
  - [ ] Run on: Desktop + Mobile simulation
  - [ ] Document scores in S44-QA-REPORT.md

